<Layout
  title="High-End & Luxury Appliance Repair Calabasas"
  description="Book Online (424) 499-7788 ★★★★★ High-End & Luxury appliance repair in Calabasas for Sub-Zero, Wolf, Miele, Thermador, La Cornue and other premium brands. Same-day or next-day service."
  structuredData={structuredData}
  ogImage="/high-end-and-luxury-appliance-repair-by-zaricci.webp"
>
  <ParallaxHeader client:idle />

  <div class="maincontent" id="webpage">
    <h2>Luxury Appliance Repair in Calabasas, CA</h2>

    <p>
      In Calabasas, appliance repair is often performed inside gated communities,
      hillside properties, canyon-adjacent homes, and carefully planned residences
      with custom kitchens and outdoor entertaining areas. Homes around Parkway
      Calabasas, Calabasas Road, Mulholland Highway, Las Virgenes Road, and Lost
      Hills Road frequently include built-in refrigerators, professional ranges,
      panel-ready dishwashers, wine storage systems, outdoor kitchens, and European
      appliances that require precise diagnostics and careful workmanship.
    </p>

    <p>
      From estate kitchens in The Oaks and Calabasas Park Estates to homes in
      Calabasas Hills, Calabasas Highlands, Mulwood, Mont Calabasas, Saratoga Hills,
      and the areas surrounding Old Town Calabasas, we provide appliance service
      designed around premium equipment and the custom finishes that surround it.
    </p>
  </div>

  <Tabs client:visible />

  <div class="maincontent" id="service">
    <section>
      <h3>Why Calabasas Homeowners Rely on ZARICCI</h3>

      <ul>
        <li>
          <strong>✅ Experienced with Major Luxury Brands</strong>
          <br />
          We service high-performance, fully integrated, and smart appliances—whether
          you are working with a dual-fuel Wolf range, a panel-ready Sub-Zero
          refrigerator, a Miele steam oven, or a premium outdoor kitchen system.
          Our technicians use a careful, brand-conscious diagnostic approach.
        </li>

        <li>
          <strong>✅ Careful Service for Custom Kitchens</strong>
          <br />
          Many Calabasas homes include custom cabinetry, stone countertops, built-in
          refrigeration, premium flooring, designer ventilation, and outdoor
          entertaining spaces. We work carefully around the installation and
          surrounding finishes.
        </li>

        <li>
          <strong>✅ OEM Parts Whenever Available</strong>
          <br />
          Your appliances are an investment. When replacement components are needed,
          we identify the appropriate OEM, manufacturer-approved, or compatible part
          for the specific appliance and model.
        </li>

        <li>
          <strong>✅ Same-Day or Next-Day Scheduling</strong>
          <br />
          We offer priority scheduling in Calabasas whenever appointment availability
          allows, with respect for your time, privacy, and home.
        </li>

        <li>
          <strong>✅ Discreet, White-Glove Repair Experience</strong>
          <br />
          We maintain a clean workspace, communicate clearly, and provide the
          professional service expected in a carefully maintained home.
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h3>Our Luxury Repair Process</h3>

      <ol>
        <li>
          <strong>Book Your Appointment</strong>
          <br />
          Call or schedule online. We will confirm your preferred time and gather
          basic information about your appliance.
        </li>

        <li>
          <strong>On-Time Arrival & Brand-Specific Diagnosis</strong>
          <br />
          Your ZARICCI technician arrives promptly and performs a careful inspection
          using the diagnostic approach appropriate for the appliance type and symptoms.
        </li>

        <li>
          <strong>Clear, Upfront Estimate</strong>
          <br />
          We explain the issue and provide a transparent quote before proceeding
          with the recommended repair.
        </li>

        <li>
          <strong>Precision Repair & Performance Testing</strong>
          <br />
          We complete the approved repair, restore appliance function, and test
          the relevant systems for proper performance.
        </li>

        <li>
          <strong>Final Walkthrough & Service Warranty</strong>
          <br />
          We clean the work area, answer your questions, and explain the warranty
          that applies to the completed service.
        </li>
      </ol>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h3>Serving Calabasas Homes, Estates & Outdoor Kitchens</h3>

      <p>
        We serve residences throughout The Oaks, Calabasas Hills, Calabasas Park
        Estates, Calabasas Highlands, Mulwood, Mont Calabasas, Saratoga Hills, and
        areas near Parkway Calabasas, Mulholland Highway, Las Virgenes Road, Lost
        Hills Road, and Old Town Calabasas. Our service is designed for gated
        communities, hillside homes, canyon-adjacent properties, and custom residences
        where precise diagnostics, clean workmanship, and discretion matter.
      </p>

      <p>
        Calabasas homes often include outdoor entertaining spaces with built-in grills,
        outdoor refrigerators, ice makers, beverage centers, side burners, pizza ovens,
        and warming drawers. We provide repair service for these outdoor kitchen
        appliances alongside the refrigeration, cooking, dishwashing, and laundry
        systems inside the home.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h3>Your Home Deserves More Than a Quick Fix</h3>

      <p>
        Your luxury appliances were selected for their performance, craftsmanship,
        and style. At <strong>ZARICCI</strong>, we deliver a repair experience that
        reflects those same values—with skill, discretion, and careful service from
        start to finish.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h3>📞 Schedule Your Luxury Appliance Repair in Calabasas Today</h3>

      <p>
        Do not wait for a small appliance issue to become a major disruption.
        <br />
        Call <strong>Luxury Appliance Repair by Zaricci</strong> or book online now
        to schedule expert service in Calabasas, CA.
      </p>

      <p>
        <strong>ZARICCI — Because Calabasas Homes Deserve World-Class Repair.</strong>
      </p>
    </section>

    <Logos client:visible />
    <Reviews client:idle />
  </div>
</Layout>